name: Standing Up
overview: From odd jobs to the hunt for viral fame, making a career in stand-up comedy isn't easy, but four friends risk everything to make the world laugh.

episodes.name: Give Us a Laugh!
episodes.overview: While struggling comic Nezir weighs a tricky job offer, his friend Aïssa tries out racy new material, and club owner Bling has a wild night onstage.

episodes.name: A Successful Touch
episodes.overview: As Aïssa's fame grows, so do the tensions at home. Nezir and Bling start on their secret project. Apolline signs up for a beginner's set at the club.

episodes.name: Black Goes with Everything
episodes.overview: Bling gets a shot at writing for TV, Aïssa draws inspiration from a run-in with the police, and Apolline asks Nezir to help her polish her act.

episodes.name: Go, Pistachio!
episodes.overview: More good news leaves Aïssa torn between two worlds. Nezir juggles a new job and a neighborhood comedy show. Apolline gets a confidence boost.

episodes.name: A Streetcar Named Nezir
episodes.overview: A mishap brings Nezir and Bling closer. Aïssa grapples with unexpected news and an uncomfortable on-air moment. Apolline's deceptions begin to unravel.
